1 require exemption under subsection (a), above, if the entire property were so used, the valuation
2 of the part so used shall be exempted is exempt from taxation.
3 (e) Real property held by an organization described in subdivision (a)(8) for a charitable
4 purpose under this section as a future site for housing housing, other than affordable rental
5 housing as defined in G.S. 105-278.7A, for individuals or families with low or moderate incomes
6 may be classified under this section for no more than 10 five years. The taxes that would
